      "value": "<p>A famous recipe from @UUID[Compendium.folken-games-fantasy-chef.folken-games-fantasy-cooking-journal-entries.JournalEntry.sqEE4iaGlPaZwFLC]{Savage Sustenance}</p><p>Provides @UUID[Compendium.pf1.spells.mz9yr5yhr0f3oqtp]{Darkvision}and Immune to Ghoul Touch / Ghoul Fever. for 4 hours.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">A velvety and creamy pudding made with a combination of whipped cream, milk, and your choice of flavors such as chocolate, vanilla, or butterscotch. Served chilled in individual cups or bowls.</span></p><img src=\"modules/folken-games-fantasy-chef/images/burrata_in_cream_arcanograph_dd_magic_item_dark.jpg\" />",
